OL,3,CTeenager arrested for attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter boy injured in rugby club fire
OL,6,FA 13-year-old boy has been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of attempted murder after
OL,8,Fanother boy was seriously hurt in a
OL,9,Ffire at a rugby club in
OL,10,FCarmarthenshire.
OL,12,FDyfed-Powys Police has told ITV News
OL,13,Fthey received a report of a fire at
OL,14,FTrimsaran Rugby Club on Saturday, 23rd
OL,15,FMay at around 6:15pm.
OL,17,FIt's believed a container was
OL,18,Fallegedly set alight deliberately, in
OL,19,Fwhich an 11-year old boy was taken to
OL,20,Fhospital with serious injuries.
