OL,3,CTeenager arrested for attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter boy injured in rugby club fire
OL,6,FThe blaze is said to have caused
OL,7,Fextensive damage to the container and
OL,8,Fits contents.
OL,10,FThe 13-year-old boy was arrested on
OL,11,Fsuspicion of arson and attempted
OL,12,Fmurder and has been released on
OL,13,Fconditional bail.
